title: Tech to tee it up at Palmetto Intercollegiate - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech to tee it up at Palmetto Intercollegiate  VT hokiesports.com
description: After competing in the Dorado Beach Collegiate, the Virginia Tech men's golf team is making the trek to South Carolina for the Palmetto Intercollegiate hosted by USC Aiken at Palmetto Golf Club (par 70, 6,617 yards), Monday-Tuesday.
